episodes.title: Empowered Liberation: Breaking Free From the NXIVM Sex Cult
episodes.description: As a multi-platform creative, Jessica is an accomplished poet, public speaker, and author. "The Untouchable Jessica Joan", made national headlines as a key witness and whistleblower against Keith Raniere and the NXVIM cult. Join us as Jessica Joan unfolds her narrative, revealing the steps she took to move forward and attain liberation after escaping the NVIVM sex cult.Follow Jessica on IG  and YouTube: @thesirenandthesunflower Ep. 04- - -Socials: Follow on IG: https://bit.ly/47rjvrUFollow on Facebook: https://bit.ly/3MVdwTXSubscribe on YouTube: https://bit.ly/3QSydBdSupport the show
